def solve(times)
  ok, ng = [0] * 3, [0] * 3
  times.each do |t|
    a, b = t.split
    h = a.split(':')[0].to_i
    m = (b.to_i - a.split(':')[1].to_i + 60) % 60
    if 11 <= h && h <= 14
      m > 8 ? ng[0] += 1 : ok[0] += 1
    elsif 18 <= h && h <= 20
      m > 8 ? ng[1] += 1 : ok[1] += 1
    elsif 0 <= h && h < 2 || 21 <= h && h <= 23
      m > 8 ? ng[2] += 1 : ok[2] += 1
    end
  end
  [ok, ng]
end

    when 18..20
      id = 1
    when 21..25
      id = 2
    end

      oks[id] += 1 if ok
    end
  end

  for i in (0..2)
    out = (totals[i] > 0) ? (100 * oks[i] / totals[i]) : 'no guest'
    puts "#{TNAMES[i]} #{out}"
  end
end
